headline: Why Moderna (MRNA) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of biotechnology company Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) jumped 4% in the morning session after the company announced positive preliminary data for its updated 2025-2026 COVID-19 vaccine, Spikevax®.

headline: How Renewed Scrutiny of Pediatric Vaccine Safety at Moderna (MRNA) Has Changed Its Investment Story
summary: In early September 2025, news emerged that Trump administration health officials planned to present claims linking COVID-19 vaccines to the deaths of about two dozen children, prompting heightened regulatory and public scrutiny of Moderna’s vaccine safety, as well as anticipated CDC advisory committee discussions and possible new vaccine eligibility restrictions.
